<h2 style="text-align: left;">Lapland Package holidays</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We have two fantastic choices for your Lapland holiday, both of which include your flights, transfers and accommodation. </span></p>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250}" title="Lapland/Finland">7 nights - Lapland Holidays</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13093023/laplandcabins-408x200.jpg" alt="lapland cabin" data-udi="umb://media/97d72def285041aeb67eba9b5a292ab6" /></p>
<p><span>Experience all that Lapland has to offer on our 7 night holidays. See the Northern lights, take a Husky ride, feed the Reindeer and ski through the forest (even visit Santa during the festive season) - this and more. </span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a}" title="Santa Breaks">3 &amp; 4 nights - Santa Breaks</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13093025/santareindeer-408x200.jpg" alt="reindeer and santa" data-udi="umb://media/0c8abbe6bcf64f2495f05065f72adc1c" /></p>
<p>Get a private meeting with Santa, take part in games with the Elves, wrap up in thermal suits, and enjoy a farewell feast - celebrate the festive season on our Lapland holidays to see Santa.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><img style="width: 0px; height: 0px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13089361/climate-action-plan-hero-838x330.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/2a04a7d8f96e4ed095539e0430ce5c35" /></p>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Where we go in Lapland</h2>
<p>We offer so many wonderful places to stay whilst your visiting Lapland, from Glass Igloos to Log Cabins. We visit three unique resorts, our <a data-udi="umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a}" title="Santa Breaks">Santa Breaks</a> holidays are available in Yllas and Levi.</p>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Levi Holidays</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13093026/glassigloo-314x193.jpg" alt="glass igloo" data-udi="umb://media/a8024a1d9eb54d05be9d349842f061c0" /></p>
<p><span style="color: #4f4f4f; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">One of the most popular resorts in Lapland, Levi boasts a wide range of accommodation, bars and restaurants as well as one of the best ski areas in Finland. For a unique experience try a night in a<span> </span></span><a style="color: #f26419; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;" data-udi="umb://document/7a950f997b0d4f868205f0e6f8e60cdf" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lapland-holidays/glass-igloo-aurora-cabin-excursion" title="Glass Igloo &amp; Aurora Cabin Excursion">thermal glass igloo. </a></p>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi">7 Nights Lapland Holiday Levi &gt;</a></h4>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/9dee14339770490983c23ccc11530d35" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9dee14339770490983c23ccc11530d35}" title="Santa Breaks in Levi">3/4 Nights Santa Breaks Levi &gt;</a></h4>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Yllas Holidays</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13090993/christmas-trees-lights-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/9770efdc5def423ba0d5914a4012148a" /></p>
<p>Comprised of two villages which are surrounded by fells, the scenery here provides the perfect backdrop for exciting Winter activities. At the end of the day feel cosy and warm, all snuggled up in our beautiful, authentic <a data-udi="umb://document/a64717f77a214ef9a7be6f05c4ca8e4f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a64717f77a214ef9a7be6f05c4ca8e4f}" title="Yllas Log Cabins">Lapland cabins. </a></p>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas">7 Nights Lapland Holiday Yllas &gt;</a></h4>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/8d7194d440db47e2b48d371f537fb9db" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8d7194d440db47e2b48d371f537fb9db}" title="Santa Breaks in Yllas">3/4 Nights Santa Breaks Yllas &gt;</a></h4>
</div>
<div></div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Saariselka Holidays</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13093030/reindeer-ride-lapland-314x193.jpg" alt="Saariselka Reindeer Ride" data-udi="umb://media/901ace978a92448d861f388bb88799a9" /></p>
<p>A<span style="color: #4f4f4f; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">n exceptionally friendly, uncommercialised resort, Saariselka is famed for its vast cross country trails and Northern Europe's longest toboggan run. You can even sleep under the magical night sky in a cosy<span> </span><a style="color: #f26419; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;" data-udi="umb://document/7a950f997b0d4f868205f0e6f8e60cdf" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lapland-holidays/glass-igloo-aurora-cabin-excursion" title="Glass Igloo &amp; Aurora Cabin Excursion">Aurora Cabin</a>.</span></p>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka">7 Nights Lapland Holiday - Saariselka &gt;</a></h4>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Things to do in Lapland</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13093028/huskies-lapland-838x320.jpg" alt="Things to do in Lapland" data-udi="umb://media/23617693233c4b15b3e6650ca9f24394" /></p>
<p>Lapland is magical in everyway, whether you want to sleep under the stars for a night in Glass Igloos or you want to speed through the forest on a Husky Ride - there are so many exciting and wonderful activities, it will be hard for you to decide - have a sneak peak of the fun things you can enjoy during your visit:</p>
